   DeVore, Melanie L., Georgia Coll \& State Univ, Dept Biol \& Environm Sci, Milledgeville, GA 31061 USA.
   Taylor, Witt, Bentley Univ, Dept Nat \& Appl Sci, Waltham, MA 02452 USA.
